    <div class="container" id="predictions">
        <h2 class="section-title">2025 Market Outlook</h2>
        
        <div class="page-content">
            <p>The cryptocurrency market in 2025 has matured significantly from previous cycles, with several key trends shaping the landscape:</p>
            
            <h2>Institutional Adoption</h2>
            <p>Major financial institutions now allocate 5-10% of their portfolios to digital assets, with Bitcoin and Ethereum ETFs surpassing $500 billion in assets under management. This mainstream acceptance has stabilized market volatility while creating sustained demand.</p>
            
            <h2>Regulatory Clarity</h2>
            <p>The regulatory framework for cryptocurrencies has matured globally, with clear guidelines in most major economies. This has encouraged institutional participation while protecting retail investors from fraudulent projects.</p>
            
            <h2>Central Bank Digital Currencies (CBDCs)</h2>
            <p>Over 30 countries have launched CBDCs, creating new opportunities for blockchain technology while also increasing competition for certain cryptocurrency use cases.</p>
            
            <h2>DeFi 3.0</h2>
            <p>Decentralized finance has evolved with improved security, scalability, and user experience. Total value locked in DeFi protocols has reached $500 billion, with real-world asset tokenization emerging as a major growth sector.</p>
            
            <h2>Web3 Integration</h2>
            <p>Web3 technologies have achieved meaningful integration with traditional platforms, creating hybrid systems that leverage blockchain benefits while maintaining familiar user experiences.</p>
        </div>
